== 製作 ==
電影原名《逃離蜘蛛頭》（{{lang|en|''Escape from Spiderhead''}}），[[Netflix|Netflix]]於2019年2月對外宣布，[[約瑟夫·柯金斯基|約瑟夫·柯金斯基]]將執導這部由[[雷特·瑞斯|雷特·瑞斯]]和[[保羅·韋尼克|保羅·韋尼克]]編劇的電影；電影改編自[[乔治·桑德斯|乔治·桑德斯]]的同名短篇小說<ref>{{cite web|title=Netflix Sets Joseph Kosinski To Follow 'Top Gun 2' With Wernick & Reese-Scripted 'Spiderhead'|url=https://deadline.com/2019/02/spiderhead-george-saunders-netflix-joseph-kosinski-rhett-reese-paul-wernick-1202547626/|last=Fleming Jr|first=Mike|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2019-02-01|access-date=2020-10-03}}</ref>。2020年9月，據報導，[[克里斯·漢斯沃|克里斯·漢斯沃]]、[[麥爾斯·泰勒|麥爾斯·泰勒]]和[[朱妮·絲莫利特|朱妮·絲莫利特]]確認參演<ref>{{cite web|title=Chris Hemsworth, Miles Teller, Jurnee Smollett Set By Netflix For Joseph Kosinski-Directed 'Spiderhead'|url=https://deadline.com/2020/09/chris-hemsworth-miles-teller-jurnee-smollett-netflix-spiderhead-movie-joseph-kosinski-1234585754/|last=Kroll|first=Justin|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2020-09-26|access-date=2020-09-26}}</ref>。

[[主要拍攝|主要拍攝]]於2020年11月上旬<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/11/miles-teller-shailene-woodley-william-hurt-the-fence-icelandic-director-grimur-hakonarson-afm-1234612900/|title=Miles Teller, Shailene Woodley & William Hurt To Star In Timely Political Satire 'The Fence' From Icelandic Director Grimur Hakonarson — AFM Hot Pic|last=Wiseman|first=Andreas|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2020-11-11|access-date=2020-11-23}}</ref>在澳大利亞[[昆士蘭州|昆士蘭州]]的[[黄金海岸_(澳大利亚)|黄金海岸]]進行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.goldcoastbulletin.com.au/entertainment/exclusive-new-chris-hemsworth-scifi-blockbuster-to-start-filming-on-the-gold-coast/news-story/f440d410218bd7babe6e2a8c541ebb61|title=Revealed: Fireworks off set as filming about to start on new Chris Hemsworth movie|last=Weston|first=Paul|work={{le|Gold Coast Bulletin|Gold Coast Bulletin}}|date=2020-11-17|access-date=2020-12-17}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
Netflix聯合CEO{{le|泰德·薩蘭多斯|Ted Sarandos}}於2021年4月證實本片定於2021年第四季度上線<ref name="ReleasePeriod">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2021/04/delayed-seasons-of-the-witcher-you-will-return-q4-2021-1234740619/|title='The Witcher', 'You' & 'Cobra Kai' Will Return To Netflix In Q4 2021|last=White|first=Peter|date=2021-04-20|access-date=2021-04-20}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{cite web|url=https://s22.q4cdn.com/959853165/files/doc_financials/2021/q1/FINAL-Q1-21-Shareholder-Letter.pdf|title=Final Q1 2021 Shareholder Letter|website=Netflix|access-date=2021-04-20|date=2021-04-20}}</ref>。2022年4月，上線日期確定為2022年6月17日<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ew.com/movies/chris-hemsworth-miles-teller-spiderhead-first-look/|title=Miles Teller is Chris Hemsworth's guinea pig in first look at new prison sci-fi film Spiderhead|first=Clark|last=Collis|website=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2022-04-21|access-date=2022-04-27}}</ref>。

== 評價 ==
《蜘蛛頭監獄》整體評價毀譽參半，其中趨向負面為主。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據119條專業評論（49條好評，70條差評），獲得新鮮度41%，平均得分5.4/10，共識評價寫道：「《蜘蛛頭監獄》的頂尖演員陣容和精心編寫的源材料，幾乎足以彌補其經常未能發揮其潜力的不足」<ref>{{Cite web|title=spiderhead|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spiderhead|website=Rotten Tomatoes|date=2022-06-23|access-date=2022-06-23|language=en|archive-date=2022-06-23|archive-url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spiderhead}}</ref>`。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]根據33條評論，獲得加權平均分數54分（滿分100分），代表「褒貶不一或中庸」<ref>{{Cite web|title=spiderhead|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/spiderhead|website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|date=2022-06-23|access-date=2022-06-23|language=en|archive-date=2022-06-23|archive-url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/spiderhead}}</ref>。

